      <div class="faq-main">

        <!-- Adoption Process -->
        <div class="faq-section" id="adoption">
          <div class="faq-section-head">
            <div class="faq-section-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>The Adoption Process</h2>
              <p>How to reserve, pay, and bring your puppy home.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-list">

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                How do I reserve a puppy?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>Browse our <a href="/available-puppies">available puppies</a>, choose the one you love, then contact us via WhatsApp, email, or our <a href="/contact">contact form</a>. We'll confirm availability and walk you through the next steps. A $200 deposit holds your puppy.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                Is the $200 deposit refundable?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>Yes. If for any reason we cannot fulfill your order (puppy health issue, etc.), your deposit is fully refunded. If you change your mind after reserving, the deposit may be applied to a future puppy from us.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                What payment methods do you accept?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>We accept Zelle, CashApp, and direct bank transfer. The $200 deposit is due at reservation; the remaining balance is due before delivery. We do not accept credit cards at this time.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                Can I visit in person before buying?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>We are a home-based breeder in Georgia and welcome pre-arranged visits. Most of our families are out-of-state — we do regular video calls so you can see your puppy live before committing. Just ask!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Health & AKC -->
        <div class="faq-section" id="health">
          <div class="faq-section-head">
            <div class="faq-section-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>Health &amp; AKC Registration</h2>
              <p>Health guarantees, genetic testing, and what comes with your puppy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-list">

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                What does the 2-year health guarantee cover?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>Our written 2-year guarantee covers life-threatening genetic defects. If your puppy is diagnosed with a covered condition within two years, we will replace the puppy or refund the purchase price. Full terms are provided with your puppy's paperwork.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                What health testing do the parents undergo?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>All parent dogs receive comprehensive genetic health screening, eye clearances (CAER), and hip evaluations (OFA). We test for hereditary conditions common in Cocker Spaniels including PRA, FN, and PFKD.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                What comes with the puppy at pickup/delivery?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <ul>
                    <li>AKC registration paperwork (limited or full, as agreed)</li>
                    <li>Vet health certificate issued within 10 days of travel</li>
                    <li>Up-to-date vaccination records</li>
                    <li>Deworming records</li>
                    <li>Microchip registration info</li>
                    <li>Written 2-year health guarantee</li>
                    <li>Puppy care starter pack (food sample, blanket with mom's scent)</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                Are the puppies microchipped?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>Yes, every puppy is microchipped before leaving us. You receive the chip registration paperwork and we'll help you transfer it to your name.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Delivery -->
        <div class="faq-section" id="delivery">
          <div class="faq-section-head">
            <div class="faq-section-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h1.125c.621 0 1.129-.504 1.09-1.124a17.902 17.902 0 00-3.213-9.193 2.056 2.056 0 00-1.58-.86H14.25M16.5 18.75h-2.25m0-11.177v-.958c0-.568-.422-1.048-.987-1.106a48.554 48.554 0 00-10.026 0 1.106 1.106 0 00-.987 1.106v7.635m12-6.677v6.677m0 4.5v-4.5m0 0h-12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>Delivery &amp; Transport</h2>
              <p>Safe puppy delivery options across the USA &amp; Canada.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-list">

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                What delivery options are available?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>We offer four delivery options:</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li><strong>Road Transport (~$170)</strong> — Ground delivery via trusted regional transport partners.</li>
                    <li><strong>Air Cargo (~$250)</strong> — Airline-regulated, climate-controlled cargo hold.</li>
                    <li><strong>Door-to-Door Ground (~$320)</strong> — Personalized delivery straight to your home.</li>
                    <li><strong>Flight Nanny (~$600)</strong> — A professional accompanies your puppy in-cabin the entire flight.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p style="margin-top:10px;">We recommend Flight Nanny for long distances. <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> and we'll suggest the best option for your location.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                Do you deliver to all 50 US states?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>Yes — we deliver to all 50 US states and across Canada. If you don't see your city on our <a href="/locations">Locations page</a>, don't worry. Just reach out and we'll arrange delivery to you.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                How does the Flight Nanny service work?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>A trained professional carries your puppy in an approved in-cabin carrier on a direct or connecting flight to your nearest major airport. You'll receive photo and text updates throughout the journey and meet the nanny at arrivals.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                Can I pick up my puppy in person?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>Absolutely! You're welcome to drive or fly to Georgia and pick up your puppy in person. Many families enjoy making a trip of it. Just let us know during the reservation process and we'll coordinate a pickup time.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- After Adoption -->
        <div class="faq-section" id="after">
          <div class="faq-section-head">
            <div class="faq-section-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h2>After Adoption</h2>
              <p>Support, feeding, and life with your Cocker Spaniel.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-list">

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                Do you offer support after the puppy comes home?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>Yes — lifetime breeder support is something we take seriously. Whether you have questions about nutrition, training, grooming, or health, our team is always reachable by WhatsApp or email. We love seeing puppy updates too!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                What food should I feed my new puppy?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>We'll include a sample of the food your puppy has been eating so you can transition gradually. We recommend a high-quality puppy food for small-to-medium breeds. Suggest a 7–10 day transition if you switch brands to avoid stomach upset.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
                Are Cocker Spaniels good with children?
                <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
              </button>
              <div class="faq-answer">
                <div class="faq-answer-inner">
                  <p>American Cocker Spaniels are known for being gentle, patient, and affectionate with children of all ages. Our puppies are home-raised around kids, which means they're already well-socialized before coming to you. They also do well with other dogs and cats.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div><!-- /faq-main -->
    </div><!-- /faq-layout -->
  </div>
</section>

